name: Zheffir Stormcaller

quests:
- dragon_eggs

description: A hardened sandsailor. Tan, leathery, dusty skin. Keeps most of his skin covered at all times to protect from the sand. Enjoys bathing, smoking and relaxing at Sahada Oasis when not out on journey across the Sea of Sands. Secretly a member of the Cerulean Society.

Burly, dark hair, waxed moustache, dirty, smells of booze and tobacco, scarred

Perception 16: tattoo of blue dragon on his right calf

To Nephi: “You are High Hamut blood, yes? You are a capable fighter?”
